      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2">Saint-Julien, Bordeaux</p>
      <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">A useful Bordeaux benchmark because it shows cassis, cedar, and real Left Bank structure without requiring first-growth money. Buy this when you want the shape of classic claret.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-wine-600 mt-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Bordeaux Blend</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-5 border border-gray-100">
